</p><p id="p_99">41.It was submitted by Mr. Ganguly that the intention of the

  parties was never to exclude the applicability of <a href="/doc/1052228/" id="a_84">Arbitration

  Act</a>, 1996. It is submitted that the expression “laws of India”

